reviewText: I grew up on Benji longer ago than I want to admit and just love seeing him on screen. Of course the films are a bit hokey now that I'm older, but who cares! It's BENJI!!!
Great movies! My son and I just love it. Thank-you
My Grandson love it!  He will watch these over and over.  Benji compared to the trash they have these days is all American.

I must have been under a rock when these priceless "movies" were made, but thank God for Joe Camp, the producer, joining with Amazon! Each one is priceless, knowing they were #3 in the country, some made without humans, showcasing the talent of a very smart dog and his humans that brought out the best in him.
